				<td class="PanelBodyAlternate"><span class="SmallBoldText">Re: What is wrong with these young bards today?<a name="4505"/></span><br><span class="SmallText"> Posted: </span><span class="SmallText">Feb 19 03 3:15 PM</span></td>
