				<td colspan="2"><span>LMAO.  I'm pretty sure that most of us could still twist at least two songs even with a hook.
<br />

<br />
Seriously though, I see where you're coming from.  Perhaps they misunderstood when I asked if they knew how to twist.  I don't know.  One thing I do know, is that if they don't start learning then they are going to end up hating the bard class.  A bard that doesn't twist is less than half as powerful as they should be.
<br />

<br />
I realize that I am somewhat biased when it comes to the bard class and that I still have a lot to learn myself.  If they were just willing to take advise then I wouldn't have had a problem with them at all.
<br />

<br />
